{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"00ededad8e","title":"中央文革与一司三司北航矿院等代表座谈时的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0d99ce979c","index":0,"year":1966,"month":12,"day":14,"articleId":"00ededad8e","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"关锋","id":"00506c3c84","type":"人物"},{"name":"陆定一","id":"107051c4e6","type":"人物"},{"name":"阎长贵","id":"269c664f91","type":"人物"},{"name":"戚本禹","id":"57434e107b","type":"人物"},{"name":"康生","id":"57eea82497","type":"人物"},{"name":"刘志坚","id":"5d13a4eb3c","type":"人物"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"王任重","id":"8b05ac46d8","type":"人物"},{"name":"聂元梓","id":"8e7eaace26","type":"人物"},{"name":"谢富治","id":"93cca4665d","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"异端思潮","id":"ca0e96a612","type":"主题"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"陈伯达","id":"e46e45351b","type":"人物"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"jqjianghua","name":"江青十年讲话汇编","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"江青，本世纪初国内老左编","files":"/books/jqjianghua.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"421124ccd3","name":"江青"},{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"},{"id":"8bb7755376","name":"康生"}]},"publication_details":{"jqjianghua":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e1564ccecb","type":"title","text":"中央文革与一司三司北航矿院等代表座谈时的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d37f23598a","type":"paragraph","text":"〖一司、三司、北航“红旗”、矿院“东方红”等单位代表参加座谈。参加座谈的还有谢富治、关锋、戚本禹、刘志坚、阎长贵同志。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9796abe275","type":"paragraph","text":"你们谈的这些情况很好，过去很少与你们座谈，直接联系少，间接联系多，以后要经常联系，我们是你们的小学生，首先向你们学习，我们要从你们这里吸取营养。","index":2,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c11835eb2b","type":"paragraph","text":"昨天与一部分中学生讲了，知道了许多事情，今天与你们谈又知道了许多事情，我们应经常和你们接触，我们相信你们会给我们许多真实的材料，这样我们头脑里可以有许多材料了，大家还准备给我们提供什么？","index":3,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2b0d4b77b9","type":"paragraph","text":"有人问：准备在十七号开个大会，象十月六号一样，内容是：","index":4,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"214320e9a9","type":"paragraph","text":"1．控诉资产阶级反动路线，重庆代表发言。","index":5,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f98f44f712","type":"paragraph","text":"2．平反问题：外地很严重，至今未平反，号召群众自己解放自己把材料抢出来平反。","index":6,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"054760a038","type":"paragraph","text":"3．一小撮人反对文革，与他们进行坚决斗争。","index":7,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ee12f3be58","type":"paragraph","text":"4．与工人结合问题。（以上四点是大意）","index":8,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8125590230","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达：从你们反映的情况看，文化革命中阶级斗争的表现，还是长期的。毛主席说：无产阶级文化大革命，是触及人们灵魂的大革命，是换脑筋的问题，从一个脑筋换成另一个脑筋，用无产阶级脑筋换资产阶级脑筋，这是件不容易的事。平反的问题，要执行中央方针政策，简单宣布平反能不能解决问题，刚才提的这个问题很值得想。材料烧毁了，也平反了，但是思想没革命。他（指当权派）思想不革命，还可以随时写黑材料，主要是解决他们的思想问题。我们也要革命，包括我在内。不革命是不可能前进的，无产阶级革命事业要不断前进，不断有新的经验出来，有许多的经验被新的经验代替了。要不断革命，不断改造，如果不懂这一点，总以为“老子天下第一”那就成了前进中的绊脚石了。","index":9,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"10ab883891","type":"paragraph","text":"你们对我们有无产阶级感情了，在有阶级的社会，所有感情是有阶级性的。你们对我们有深厚的无产阶级感情，我们很感激，感谢你们。同时你们还要不断鞭策我们，帮我们改正。我们不可免地有缺点有错误。这和踢开中央文革、解散中央文革是两回事。你们要中央文革帮助，我们也要你们帮助。动脑筋想一想我们说得对不对？不对的可以批判。","index":10,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5056a19a8b","type":"paragraph","text":"我们要在实践中总结经验，毛主席说过，中国共产党有三大作风，一条是理论联系实际的作风，一条是群众路线，一条是批评与自我批评。这是我党同一切剥削阶级区别的标志，我们不可能没错，有错必须改，所以要批评和自我批评的勇气。","index":11,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c3138b0c21","type":"paragraph","text":"康生、江青等同志的插话","index":12,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4a2df60ecc","type":"paragraph","text":"有人说：矿院反映说：“批判戚本禹联络站已公开解散了......”。","index":13,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"87f086631a","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：对反革命分子实行严厉镇压，这是最大民主，......李洪山就是反革命小头目。","index":14,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c043cc62bb","type":"paragraph","text":"有人反映：保守派党员特别多。","index":15,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"67bc98e0c6","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达插话：共产党员不是买到的，如果可以买到就成假的了。","index":16,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7eb4481c00","type":"paragraph","text":"有人问：清华有人叫嚣要为陆定一翻案，大家贴了许多大字报，保守派就说是不让他们发言。大家组织起来写大字报，开辩论会对反革命逆流进行反击，有人说是一言堂。（大意）","index":17,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"77c3a4fd67","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：首先搞清什么是无产阶级专政问题。","index":18,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7936b46d43","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：大民主是广大人民的民主，对反革命分子要实行专政。一言堂，只有革命人民的言论自由，没有无产阶级专政就没有大民主，大民主是巩固无产阶级专政的。","index":19,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"62bcaed4fd","type":"paragraph","text":"矿院有人说：保守派说：我们揪文革、戚本禹等是炮打无产阶级司令部，那么你们揪王任重也是炮打无产阶级司令部。","index":20,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"11aedcee8d","type":"paragraph","text":"关锋：王任重在北京，湖北、湖南情况与中央文革没关系，没汇报过文革不负责任。轰他不算炮打无产阶级司令部。","index":21,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6da9d46a2e","type":"paragraph","text":"还有人反映：我校秋后算帐派说：“你们闹吧！秋后再算账。”","index":22,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2ef2b3d09c","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：现在不是算我们的帐，是我们算他们的帐。","index":23,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4d1d17dc70","type":"paragraph","text":"有人问：有人造谣，毛主席在一次部长会议上承认了三点错误：1．支持聂元梓的大字报，2．支持红卫兵，3．支持革命大串连。","index":24,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1b0e59e393","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：这是反革命造谣。这些话是主席对那些走资本主义道路当权派说的，（即：有些当权派（走资本主义道路的）说，我就是这样革命的，就是支持聂元梓，支持了红卫兵，支持了大串联；这就是我的“罪”）（主席是引用他们的话对他们说的。）","index":25,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"647bcfa1ee","type":"paragraph","text":"有人反映：我们斗争了很长时间，把×××的官罢了，大家觉得胜利了（大意）。","index":26,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"417c56d284","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：把官罢了，还要斗。光罢官不行，黑东西没抖出来，不解决问题，要斗。","index":27,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ca30631ce7","type":"paragraph","text":"有人反映：关于给林总提意见，攻击林总的事。","index":28,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"281a7d5979","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：攻击林总是否叫群众？凡是反对林总和毛主席的就是反革命。他们不是群众，是群众的敌人，是他们与群众做斗争。对中央文革态度的辩论是要不要无产阶级专政的问题。","index":29,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6278c74de7","type":"paragraph","text":"矿院东方红反映：多数派说（保守派），你们少数派不怕当反革命，我们也不怕当反革命。","index":30,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6273cd12b7","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：别忘了咱们是无产阶级专政。又说：有人把反对林总的标语，传单隔墙投到林总家里去，你们也可以给他们贴，你们认为他们谁是后台，可以给他贴，揪对不对？","index":31,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"566002415d","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达：对！（鼓掌）","index":32,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e2e6ff8fed","type":"paragraph","text":"有人反映：保守派党员特别多。","index":33,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a65f2f15d1","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达插话：共产党员不是买到的，如果可以买到，就成了假的了。","index":34,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0f4b6f4bd4","type":"paragraph","text":"有人问：清华有人叫嚣要为陆定一翻案，大家贴了许多大字报，保守派就说是不让他们发言。大家组织起来写大字报，开辩论会对反革命逆流进行反击，有人说是一言堂。（大意）","index":35,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ccfb28ed21","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：首先搞清什么是无产阶级专政的问题。","index":36,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a49c99f64a","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：大民主是广大人民的民主，对反革命分子要实行专政；一言堂只有革命人民的言论自由，没有反革命言论自由；没有无产阶级专政，就没有大民主，大民主是巩固无产阶级专政的。","index":37,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"95e070b160","type":"paragraph","text":"矿院有人说：保守派说“我们揪中央文革戚本禹等是炮轰无产阶级司令部，那末你们揪王任重也是炮轰无产阶级革命司令部。”","index":38,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"be1a151c72","type":"paragraph","text":"关锋：王任重在北京、湖北、湖南情况与中央文革没关系，没汇报过，文革不负责任。轰他不算炮打无产阶级司令部。","index":39,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6a8b452aed","type":"paragraph","text":"还有人反映：我校秋后算账派说“你们闹吧！秋后再算账。”江青：现在不是算我们的账，是我们算他们的账。","index":40,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"57fc6def4a","type":"paragraph","text":"有人问：有人造谣，毛主席在一次部长会议上承认了三点错误：1、支持聂元梓大字报；2、支持红卫兵；3、支持革命大串联。","index":41,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d9e4662bab","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：这是反革命造谣。这些话，是主席对那些走资本主义道路的当权派这样说的：“我就是这样革命的，就是支持聂元梓、支持了红卫兵、支持了大串联，这就是我的罪。”（主席是引用他们的话对他们说的。）","index":42,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"747dda8f28","type":"paragraph","text":"有人反映：我们斗争了很长时间，把×××的官罢了，大家觉得胜利了。（大意）","index":43,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e00d884a00","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：把官罢了还要斗，光罢官不行，黑东西没抖出来，不解决问题。","index":44,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a1cc4ee20f","type":"paragraph","text":"有人反映：关于给林总提意见，攻击林总的事。","index":45,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aa4379c5ba","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：攻击林总是否叫群众？凡是反对林总和毛主席的就是反革命。他们不是群众，是群众的敌人，是他们与群众做斗争。对中央文革态度的辩论是要不要无产阶级专政的问题。","index":46,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"70b61e6b63","type":"paragraph","text":"矿院“东方红”反映：多数派（保守派）说“你们少数人不怕当反革命，我们也怕！”","index":47,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"25884e319e","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：别忘了咱们是无产阶级专政。有人把反对林总的标语、传单隔墙扔到林总家里去，你们也可以给他们贴，你们认为他们谁是后台，可以给他贴，揪对不对？","index":48,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"29bd5390f7","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达：对！（鼓掌）","index":49,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c62da18731","type":"paragraph","text":"（首都大专院校红卫兵第一司令部战士 翟兰朝整理）","index":50,"publicationId":"jqjianghua","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":118,"end":115}},"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"04685fe729","type":"paragraph","text":"有人反映：关于给林总提意见，攻击林总的事。","index":47,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"078a65969c","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达插话：共产党员不是买到的，如果可以买到，就成了假的了。","index":35,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"08a021e8a8","type":"paragraph","text":"矿院东方红反映：多数派说（保守派），你们少数派不怕当反革命，我们也不怕当反革命。","index":31,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"091e6a7956","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：首先搞清什么是无产阶级专政的问题。","index":37,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0bb760773d","type":"paragraph","text":"〖一司、三司、北航“红旗”、矿院“东方红”等单位代表参加座谈。参加座谈的还有谢富治、关锋、戚本禹、刘志坚、阎长贵同志。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0cece6ae9c","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：这是反革命造谣。这些话，是主席对那些走资本主义道路的当权派这样说的：“我就是这样革命的，就是支持聂元梓、支持了红卫兵、支持了大串联，这就是我的罪。”（主席是引用他们的话对他们说的。）","index":44,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"19e650f2bd","type":"paragraph","text":"3．一小撮人反对文革，与他们进行坚决斗争。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1b6d6e2468","type":"paragraph","text":"4．与工人结合问题。（以上四点是大意）","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1b761d378b","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：把官罢了还要斗，光罢官不行，黑东西没抖出来，不解决问题。","index":46,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"26158690af","type":"title","text":"中央文革与一司三司北航矿院等代表座谈时的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"34b713af03","type":"paragraph","text":"昨天与一部分中学生讲了，知道了许多事情，今天与你们谈又知道了许多事情，我们应经常和你们接触，我们相信你们会给我们许多真实的材料，这样我们头脑里可以有许多材料了，大家还准备给我们提供什么？","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3c178d3a5a","type":"paragraph","text":"有人反映：关于给林总提意见，攻击林总的事。","index":29,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3f9c50fd05","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：这是反革命造谣。这些话是主席对那些走资本主义道路当权派说的，（即：有些当权派（走资本主义道路的）说，我就是这样革命的，就是支持聂元梓，支持了红卫兵，支持了大串联；这就是我的“罪”）（主席是引用他们的话对他们说的。）","index":26,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"461a27ab56","type":"paragraph","text":"有人反映：我们斗争了很长时间，把×××的官罢了，大家觉得胜利了。（大意）","index":45,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4b465e25bb","type":"paragraph","text":"有人说：矿院反映说：“批判戚本禹联络站已公开解散了……”。","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5ec1334433","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：别忘了咱们是无产阶级专政。又说：有人把反对林总的标语，传单隔墙投到林总家里去，你们也可以给他们贴，你们认为他们谁是后台，可以给他贴，揪对不对？","index":32,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5fbfd34f83","type":"paragraph","text":"有人问：清华有人叫嚣要为陆定一翻案，大家贴了许多大字报，保守派就说是不让他们发言。大家组织起来写大字报，开辩论会对反革命逆流进行反击，有人说是一言堂。（大意）","index":36,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"61963b18a7","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：大民主是广大人民的民主，对反革命分子要实行专政。一言堂，只有革命人民的言论自由，没有无产阶级专政就没有大民主，大民主是巩固无产阶级专政的。","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"66d8ca8b9c","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达插话：共产党员不是买到的，如果可以买到就成假的了。","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6c2a1f94d9","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：现在不是算我们的帐，是我们算他们的帐。","index":24,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6d8f92b9f4","type":"paragraph","text":"同时你们还要不断鞭策我们，帮我们改正。我们不可免地有缺点有错误。这和踢开中央文革、解散中央文革是两回事。你们要中央文革帮助，我们也要你们帮助。动脑筋想一想我们说得对不对？不对的可以批判。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"70747fab56","type":"paragraph","text":"矿院有人说：保守派说“我们揪中央文革戚本禹等是炮轰无产阶级司令部，那末你们揪王任重也是炮轰无产阶级革命司令部。”","index":39,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"70de73e83c","type":"paragraph","text":"（首都大专院校红卫兵第一司令部战士  翟兰朝整理）","index":52,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7955baeaad","type":"paragraph","text":"有人反映：保守派党员特别多。","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7f27dff4f3","type":"paragraph","text":"有人问：有人造谣，毛主席在一次部长会议上承认了三点错误：1、支持聂元梓大字报；2、支持红卫兵；3、支持革命大串联。","index":43,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8276a49d3a","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：现在不是算我们的账，是我们算他们的账。","index":42,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"886650f39a","type":"paragraph","text":"有人问：准备在十七号开个大会，象十月六号一样，内容是：","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"891989d171","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达：从你们反映的情况看，文化革命中阶级斗争的表现，还是长期的。毛主席说：无产阶级文化大革命，是触及人们灵魂的大革命，是换脑筋的问题，从一个脑筋换成另一个脑筋，用无产阶级脑筋换资产阶级脑筋，这是件不容易的事。平反的问题，要执行中央方针政策，简单宣布平反能不能解决问题，刚才提的这个问题很值得想。材料烧毁了，也平反了，但是思想没革命。他（指当权派）思想不革命，还可以随时写黑材料，主要是解决他们的思想问题。我们也要革命，包括我在内。不革命是不可能前进的，无产阶级革命事业要不断前进，不断有新的经验出来，有许多的经验被新的经验代替了。要不断革命，不断改造，如果不懂这一点，总以为“老子天下第一”那就成了前进中的绊脚石了。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"90cc31af0e","type":"paragraph","text":"我们要在实践中总结经验，毛主席说过，中国共产党有三大作风，一条是理论联系实际的作风，一条是群众路线，一条是批评与自我批评。这是我党同一切剥削阶级区别的标志，我们不可能没错，有错必须改，所以要批评和自我批评的勇气。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"96808adccd","type":"paragraph","text":"还有人反映：我校秋后算账派说“你们闹吧！秋后再算账。”","index":41,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"977a7ec313","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：对反革命分子实行严厉镇压，这是最大民主，……李洪山就是反革命小头目。","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9a7c54168f","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达：对！（鼓掌）","index":51,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9b9bb7b037","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：首先搞清什么是无产阶级专政问题。","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9f0e8695ef","type":"paragraph","text":"2．平反问题：外地很严重，至今未平反，号召群众自己解放自己把材料抢出来平反。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a0b892de53","type":"paragraph","text":"1．控诉资产阶级反动路线，重庆代表发言。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a334afb39e","type":"paragraph","text":"还有人反映：我校秋后算帐派说：“你们闹吧！秋后再算账。”","index":23,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a825d5854d","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：把官罢了，还要斗。光罢官不行，黑东西没抖出来，不解决问题，要斗。","index":28,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b43e0221f2","type":"paragraph","text":"有人问：有人造谣，毛主席在一次部长会议上承认了三点错误：1．支持聂元梓的大字报，2．支持红卫兵，3．支持革命大串连。","index":25,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b7dd591ad2","type":"paragraph","text":"江青：别忘了咱们是无产阶级专政。有人把反对林总的标语、传单隔墙扔到林总家里去，你们也可以给他们贴，你们认为他们谁是后台，可以给他贴，揪对不对？","index":50,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"be2f534780","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达：对！（鼓掌）","index":33,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c13bf742d7","type":"paragraph","text":"你们对我们有无产阶级感情了，在有阶级的社会，所有感情是有阶级性的。你们对我们有深厚的无产阶级感情，我们很感激，感谢你们。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c328c3ecc2","type":"paragraph","text":"关锋：王任重在北京，湖北、湖南情况与中央文革没关系，没汇报过文革不负责任。轰他不算炮打无产阶级司令部。","index":22,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ca4c620ffa","type":"paragraph","text":"矿院“东方红”反映：多数派（保守派）说“你们少数人不怕当反革命，我们也怕！”","index":49,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cad40ce691","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：大民主是广大人民的民主，对反革命分子要实行专政；一言堂只有革命人民的言论自由，没有反革命言论自由；没有无产阶级专政，就没有大民主，大民主是巩固无产阶级专政的。","index":38,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ce1220300e","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：攻击林总是否叫群众？凡是反对林总和毛主席的就是反革命。他们不是群众，是群众的敌人，是他们与群众做斗争。对中央文革态度的辩论是要不要无产阶级专政的问题。","index":30,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d26539908c","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：攻击林总是否叫群众？凡是反对林总和毛主席的就是反革命。他们不是群众，是群众的敌人，是他们与群众做斗争。对中央文革态度的辩论是要不要无产阶级专政的问题。","index":48,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d7f925138f","type":"paragraph","text":"有人反映：我们斗争了很长时间，把×××的官罢了，大家觉得胜利了（大意）。","index":27,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e22ef892a8","type":"paragraph","text":"你们谈的这些情况很好，过去很少与你们座谈，直接联系少，间接联系多，以后要经常联系，我们是你们的小学生，首先向你们学习，我们要从你们这里吸取营养。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e49c735fd4","type":"paragraph","text":"矿院有人说：保守派说：我们揪文革、戚本禹等是炮打无产阶级司令部，那么你们揪王任重也是炮打无产阶级司令部。","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e4c892d754","type":"paragraph","text":"有人问：清华有人叫嚣要为陆定一翻案，大家贴了许多大字报，保守派就说是不让他们发言。大家组织起来写大字报，开辩论会对反革命逆流进行反击，有人说是一言堂。（大意）","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eb0d2c1c4b","type":"paragraph","text":"有人反映：保守派党员特别多。","index":34,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f7a6f9c587","type":"paragraph","text":"康生、江青等同志的插话","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fdd7bb9d57","type":"paragraph","text":"关锋：王任重在北京、湖北、湖南情况与中央文革没关系，没汇报过，文革不负责任。轰他不算炮打无产阶级司令部。","index":40,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"00ededad8e","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}